    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793240/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.poster.avif?t=1661307641\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793240/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.webm?t=1661307641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793240/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.mp4?t=1661307641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Several number cubes on your screen and your challenge is: destroy them all at once!<br><br>For this you must drop the balls in the right position and direction to find the perfect trajectory<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenge yourself at each level with new mechanics</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Walls, tunnels and cannons will challenge your physical intuition<br></li><li>New mechanics like revolving walls and moving cubes will challenge your accuracy</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>NEW! </strong>Level Editor</h2><strong>Create your own levels with the new level editor</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>There are several options of cubes, walls, tunnels and cannons for you to create levels and challenge yourself in your own way<br></li><li>Unlock all features by completing levels<br></li><li>Includes option to save created levels</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Addictive new events</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>New visual effects in all mechanics<br></li><li>Various visual and sound effects will explode your screen with addictive events<br></li><li>Make the most of stereo sound effects </li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RESOURCES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>New visual effects in all mechanics<br></li><li>New mechanics like revolving walls and moving cubes<br></li><li>New original soundtrack<br></li><li>59 new exclusive levels<br></li><li>New level editor with save option</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Other resources</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Customization: Change the game color to the one you like best<br></li><li>Steam Cloud: Save game to cloud<br></li><li>Steam Achievements: 59 Steam achievements</li></ul>",
